{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":536,"text":"So I wanted to tell a story"},{"time":1819,"text":"that really obsessed me when I was writing my new book,"},{"time":5291,"text":"and it's a story of something that happened"},{"time":8838,"text":"3,000 years ago,"},{"time":10411,"text":"when the Kingdom of Israel was in its infancy."},{"time":13638,"text":"And it takes place in an area called the Shephelah"},{"time":16370,"text":"in what is now Israel."},{"time":18700,"text":"And the reason the story obsessed me is that"},{"time":20948,"text":"I thought I understood it, and then I went back over it"},{"time":24034,"text":"and I realized that I didn't understand it at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28140,"text":"Ancient Palestine had a -- along its eastern border,"},{"time":32957,"text":"there's a mountain range."},{"time":34273,"text":"Still same is true of Israel today."},{"time":36132,"text":"And in the mountain range are all of the ancient cities"},{"time":39065,"text":"of that region, so Jerusalem, Bethlehem, Hebron."},{"time":43523,"text":"And then there's a coastal plain"},{"time":45748,"text":"along the Mediterranean, where Tel Aviv is now."},{"time":49103,"text":"And connecting the mountain range with the coastal plain"},{"time":52503,"text":"is an area called the Shephelah,"},{"time":54436,"text":"which is a series of valleys and ridges that run east to west,"},{"time":58855,"text":"and you can follow the Shephelah, go through the Shephelah"},{"time":62034,"text":"to get from the coastal plain to the mountains."},{"time":64787,"text":"And the Shephelah, if you've been to Israel, you'll know"},{"time":66481,"text":"it's just about the most beautiful part of Israel."},{"time":68889,"text":"It's gorgeous, with forests of oak"},{"time":71807,"text":"and wheat fields and vineyards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74222,"text":"But more importantly, though, in the history of that region,"},{"time":77601,"text":"it's served, it's had a real strategic function,"},{"time":81366,"text":"and that is, it is the means by which hostile armies"},{"time":84279,"text":"on the coastal plain find their way,"},{"time":86862,"text":"get up into the mountains and threaten those living in the mountains."},{"time":90484,"text":"And 3,000 years ago, that's exactly what happens."},{"time":93511,"text":"The Philistines, who are the biggest of enemies"},{"time":97788,"text":"of the Kingdom of Israel,"},{"time":99290,"text":"are living in the coastal plain."},{"time":101002,"text":"They're originally from Crete. They're a seafaring people."},{"time":104298,"text":"And they may start to make their way"},{"time":106721,"text":"through one of the valleys of the Shephelah"},{"time":108961,"text":"up into the mountains,"},{"time":110128,"text":"because what they want to do is occupy the highland area"},{"time":112384,"text":"right by Bethlehem and split the Kingdom of Israel in two."},{"time":116385,"text":"And the Kingdom of Israel, which is headed by King Saul,"},{"time":119650,"text":"obviously catches wind of this,"},{"time":121383,"text":"and Saul brings his army down from the mountains"},{"time":124252,"text":"and he confronts the Philistines in the Valley of Elah,"},{"time":127907,"text":"one of the most beautiful of the valleys of the Shephelah."},{"time":130365,"text":"And the Israelites dig in along the northern ridge,"},{"time":133233,"text":"and the Philistines dig in along the southern ridge,"},{"time":137490,"text":"and the two armies just sit there for weeks"},{"time":140225,"text":"and stare at each other, because they're deadlocked."},{"time":142347,"text":"Neither can attack the other, because to attack the other side"},{"time":144820,"text":"you've got to come down the mountain into the valley"},{"time":148076,"text":"and then up the other side, and you're completely exposed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150593,"text":"So finally, to break the deadlock,"},{"time":152785,"text":"the Philistines send their mightiest warrior"},{"time":155999,"text":"down into the valley floor, and he calls out"},{"time":158476,"text":"and he says to the Israelites,"},{"time":159932,"text":"\"Send your mightiest warrior down,"},{"time":162560,"text":"and we'll have this out, just the two of us.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":164567,"text":"This was a tradition in ancient warfare called single combat."},{"time":168402,"text":"It was a way of settling disputes"},{"time":170197,"text":"without incurring the bloodshed of a major battle."},{"time":174321,"text":"And the Philistine who is sent down,"},{"time":177281,"text":"their mighty warrior, is a giant."},{"time":179448,"text":"He's 6 foot 9."},{"time":181223,"text":"He's outfitted head to toe in this glittering bronze armor,"},{"time":185936,"text":"and he's got a sword and he's got a javelin"},{"time":188995,"text":"and he's got his spear. He is absolutely terrifying."},{"time":191723,"text":"And he's so terrifying that none of the Israelite soldiers want to fight him."},{"time":196213,"text":"It's a death wish, right? There's no way they think they can take him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200848,"text":"And finally the only person who will come forward"},{"time":203141,"text":"is this young shepherd boy,"},{"time":205652,"text":"and he goes up to Saul and he says, \"I'll fight him.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":208330,"text":"And Saul says, \"You can't fight him. That's ridiculous."},{"time":211448,"text":"You're this kid. This is this mighty warrior.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":213770,"text":"But the shepherd is adamant. He says, \"No, no, no,"},{"time":216193,"text":"you don't understand, I have been defending my flock"},{"time":219186,"text":"against lions and wolves for years. I think I can do it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":223355,"text":"And Saul has no choice. He's got no one else who's come forward."},{"time":226569,"text":"So he says, \"All right.\""},{"time":227910,"text":"And then he turns to the kid, and he says,"},{"time":229122,"text":"\"But you've got to wear this armor. You can't go as you are.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":232816,"text":"So he tries to give the shepherd his armor,"},{"time":235219,"text":"and the shepherd says, \"No.\""},{"time":236470,"text":"He says, \"I can't wear this stuff.\""},{"time":238883,"text":"The Biblical verse is, \"I cannot wear this for I have not proved it,\""},{"time":242957,"text":"meaning, \"I've never worn armor before. You've got to be crazy.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":246134,"text":"So he reaches down instead on the ground"},{"time":248740,"text":"and picks up five stones"},{"time":250495,"text":"and puts them in his shepherd's bag"},{"time":252956,"text":"and starts to walk down the mountainside to meet the giant."},{"time":257468,"text":"And the giant sees this figure approaching,"},{"time":259674,"text":"and calls out, \"Come to me so I can feed your flesh"},{"time":262817,"text":"to the birds of the heavens and the beasts of the field.\""},{"time":266794,"text":"He issues this kind of taunt towards this person"},{"time":270229,"text":"coming to fight him."},{"time":271964,"text":"And the shepherd draws closer and closer,"},{"time":275310,"text":"and the giant sees that he's carrying a staff."},{"time":278298,"text":"That's all he's carrying."},{"time":279470,"text":"Instead of a weapon, just this shepherd's staff,"},{"time":281338,"text":"and he says -- he's insulted --"},{"time":283910,"text":"\"Am I a dog that you would come to me with sticks?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":287267,"text":"And the shepherd boy takes one of his stones"},{"time":290330,"text":"out of his pocket, puts it in his sling"},{"time":293570,"text":"and rolls it around and lets it fly"},{"time":295865,"text":"and it hits the giant right between the eyes --"},{"time":298266,"text":"right here, in his most vulnerable spot --"},{"time":300364,"text":"and he falls down either dead or unconscious,"},{"time":303685,"text":"and the shepherd boy runs up and takes his sword"},{"time":306179,"text":"and cuts off his head,"},{"time":307865,"text":"and the Philistines see this and they turn and they just run."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313416,"text":"And of course, the name of the giant is Goliath"},{"time":317777,"text":"and the name of the shepherd boy is David,"},{"time":320306,"text":"and the reason that story has obsessed me"},{"time":323436,"text":"over the course of writing my book"},{"time":324874,"text":"is that everything I thought I knew about that story"},{"time":327966,"text":"turned out to be wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":330717,"text":"So David, in that story, is supposed to be the underdog, right?"},{"time":334505,"text":"In fact, that term, David and Goliath,"},{"time":336642,"text":"has entered our language as a metaphor for"},{"time":339623,"text":"improbable victories"},{"time":341161,"text":"by some weak party over someone far stronger."},{"time":344272,"text":"Now why do we call David an underdog?"},{"time":346462,"text":"Well, we call him an underdog because he's a kid,"},{"time":349937,"text":"a little kid, and Goliath is this big, strong giant."},{"time":353473,"text":"We also call him an underdog"},{"time":355128,"text":"because Goliath is an experienced warrior,"},{"time":359050,"text":"and David is just a shepherd."},{"time":360986,"text":"But most importantly, we call him an underdog"},{"time":363336,"text":"because all he has is -- it's that Goliath is outfitted with"},{"time":368346,"text":"all of this modern weaponry,"},{"time":370351,"text":"this glittering coat of armor"},{"time":372127,"text":"and a sword and a javelin and a spear,"},{"time":375962,"text":"and all David has is this sling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379792,"text":"Well, let's start there with the phrase"},{"time":381490,"text":"\"All David has is this sling,\""},{"time":383934,"text":"because that's the first mistake that we make."},{"time":386801,"text":"In ancient warfare, there are three kinds of warriors."},{"time":390358,"text":"There's cavalry, men on horseback and with chariots."},{"time":393789,"text":"There's heavy infantry, which are foot soldiers,"},{"time":396915,"text":"armed foot soldiers with swords and shields"},{"time":399805,"text":"and some kind of armor."},{"time":401305,"text":"And there's artillery, and artillery are archers,"},{"time":404533,"text":"but, more importantly, slingers."},{"time":406705,"text":"And a slinger is someone who has a leather pouch"},{"time":409766,"text":"with two long cords attached to it,"},{"time":412563,"text":"and they put a projectile, either a rock or a lead ball,"},{"time":415765,"text":"inside the pouch, and they whirl it around like this"},{"time":418886,"text":"and they let one of the cords go,"},{"time":421529,"text":"and the effect is to send the projectile forward"},{"time":425399,"text":"towards its target."},{"time":428704,"text":"That's what David has, and it's important to understand"},{"time":431439,"text":"that that sling is not a slingshot."},{"time":434286,"text":"It's not this, right? It's not a child's toy."},{"time":436905,"text":"It's in fact an incredibly devastating weapon."},{"time":440730,"text":"When David rolls it around like this,"},{"time":443706,"text":"he's turning the sling around probably"},{"time":446935,"text":"at six or seven revolutions per second,"},{"time":449607,"text":"and that means that when the rock is released,"},{"time":453452,"text":"it's going forward really fast,"},{"time":455652,"text":"probably 35 meters per second."},{"time":457425,"text":"That's substantially faster than a baseball"},{"time":460990,"text":"thrown by even the finest of baseball pitchers."},{"time":464623,"text":"More than that, the stones in the Valley of Elah"},{"time":468506,"text":"were not normal rocks. They were barium sulphate,"},{"time":471162,"text":"which are rocks twice the density of normal stones."},{"time":474481,"text":"If you do the calculations on the ballistics,"},{"time":477118,"text":"on the stopping power of the rock fired from David's sling,"},{"time":481002,"text":"it's roughly equal to the stopping power"},{"time":483323,"text":"of a [.45 caliber] handgun."},{"time":486880,"text":"This is an incredibly devastating weapon."},{"time":489874,"text":"Accuracy, we know from historical records"},{"time":494472,"text":"that slingers -- experienced slingers could hit"},{"time":498970,"text":"and maim or even kill a target at distances of up to 200 yards."},{"time":504993,"text":"From medieval tapestries, we know that slingers"},{"time":507963,"text":"were capable of hitting birds in flight."},{"time":510321,"text":"They were incredibly accurate."},{"time":512755,"text":"When David lines up -- and he's not 200 yards away from Goliath,"},{"time":516312,"text":"he's quite close to Goliath --"},{"time":517921,"text":"when he lines up and fires that thing at Goliath,"},{"time":521336,"text":"he has every intention and every expectation"},{"time":524398,"text":"of being able to hit Goliath at his most vulnerable spot"},{"time":527101,"text":"between his eyes."},{"time":528429,"text":"If you go back over the history of ancient warfare,"},{"time":530445,"text":"you will find time and time again"},{"time":533257,"text":"that slingers were the decisive factor against infantry"},{"time":537260,"text":"in one kind of battle or another."}]},{"cues":[{"time":542285,"text":"So what's Goliath? He's heavy infantry,"},{"time":546181,"text":"and his expectation when he challenges the Israelites to a duel"},{"time":551380,"text":"is that he's going to be fighting another heavy infantryman."},{"time":555235,"text":"When he says, \"Come to me that I might"},{"time":557406,"text":"feed your flesh to the birds of the heavens and the beasts of the field,\""},{"time":560358,"text":"the key phrase is \"Come to me.\""},{"time":562358,"text":"Come up to me because we're going to fight,"},{"time":564496,"text":"hand to hand, like this."},{"time":566207,"text":"Saul has the same expectation."},{"time":568335,"text":"David says, \"I want to fight Goliath,\""},{"time":570694,"text":"and Saul tries to give him his armor,"},{"time":572515,"text":"because Saul is thinking, \"Oh, when you say 'fight Goliath,'"},{"time":575242,"text":"you mean 'fight him in hand-to-hand combat,'"},{"time":578509,"text":"infantry on infantry.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":580697,"text":"But David has absolutely no expectation."},{"time":583671,"text":"He's not going to fight him that way. Why would he?"},{"time":586222,"text":"He's a shepherd. He's spent his entire career"},{"time":589230,"text":"using a sling to defend his flock against lions and wolves."},{"time":593443,"text":"That's where his strength lies."},{"time":595193,"text":"So here he is, this shepherd, experienced"},{"time":597725,"text":"in the use of a devastating weapon,"},{"time":599764,"text":"up against this lumbering giant"},{"time":602158,"text":"weighed down by a hundred pounds of armor"},{"time":605458,"text":"and these incredibly heavy weapons"},{"time":606959,"text":"that are useful only in short-range combat."},{"time":610056,"text":"Goliath is a sitting duck. He doesn't have a chance."},{"time":614793,"text":"So why do we keep calling David an underdog,"},{"time":617599,"text":"and why do we keep referring to his victory as improbable?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":623423,"text":"There's a second piece of this that's important."},{"time":626263,"text":"It's not just that we misunderstand David"},{"time":629661,"text":"and his choice of weaponry."},{"time":631566,"text":"It's also that we profoundly misunderstand Goliath."},{"time":634905,"text":"Goliath is not what he seems to be."},{"time":638139,"text":"There's all kinds of hints of this in the Biblical text,"},{"time":642127,"text":"things that are in retrospect quite puzzling"},{"time":644932,"text":"and don't square with his image as this mighty warrior."},{"time":648709,"text":"So to begin with, the Bible says that Goliath"},{"time":652086,"text":"is led onto the valley floor by an attendant."},{"time":656051,"text":"Now that is weird, right?"},{"time":658260,"text":"Here is this mighty warrior"},{"time":660390,"text":"challenging the Israelites to one-on-one combat."},{"time":663197,"text":"Why is he being led by the hand"},{"time":665909,"text":"by some young boy, presumably,"},{"time":668959,"text":"to the point of combat?"},{"time":671421,"text":"Secondly, the Bible story makes special note"},{"time":675775,"text":"of how slowly Goliath moves,"},{"time":678864,"text":"another odd thing to say when you're describing"},{"time":680890,"text":"the mightiest warrior known to man at that point."},{"time":684940,"text":"And then there's this whole weird thing"},{"time":686763,"text":"about how long it takes Goliath to react"},{"time":690575,"text":"to the sight of David."},{"time":692571,"text":"So David's coming down the mountain,"},{"time":695349,"text":"and he's clearly not preparing for hand-to-hand combat."},{"time":699286,"text":"There is nothing about him that says,"},{"time":701254,"text":"\"I am about to fight you like this.\""},{"time":703288,"text":"He's not even carrying a sword."},{"time":705019,"text":"Why does Goliath not react to that?"},{"time":707701,"text":"It's as if he's oblivious to what's going on that day."},{"time":711929,"text":"And then there's that strange comment he makes to David:"},{"time":715876,"text":"\"Am I a dog that you should come to me with sticks?\""},{"time":720171,"text":"Sticks? David only has one stick."}]},{"cues":[{"time":723994,"text":"Well, it turns out that there's been a great deal"},{"time":726253,"text":"of speculation within the medical community over the years"},{"time":729294,"text":"about whether there is something"},{"time":731820,"text":"fundamentally wrong with Goliath,"},{"time":734709,"text":"an attempt to make sense of all of those apparent anomalies."},{"time":738118,"text":"There have been many articles written."},{"time":739280,"text":"The first one was in 1960 in the Indiana Medical Journal,"},{"time":743274,"text":"and it started a chain of speculation"},{"time":745629,"text":"that starts with an explanation for Goliath's height."},{"time":748752,"text":"So Goliath is head and shoulders above"},{"time":751675,"text":"all of his peers in that era,"},{"time":753837,"text":"and usually when someone is that far out of the norm,"},{"time":757819,"text":"there's an explanation for it."},{"time":759416,"text":"So the most common form of giantism"},{"time":762649,"text":"is a condition called acromegaly,"},{"time":765384,"text":"and acromegaly is caused by a benign tumor"},{"time":768287,"text":"on your pituitary gland"},{"time":770790,"text":"that causes an overproduction of human growth hormone."},{"time":773506,"text":"And throughout history, many of the most famous giants"},{"time":777065,"text":"have all had acromegaly."},{"time":778834,"text":"So the tallest person of all time"},{"time":780898,"text":"was a guy named Robert Wadlow"},{"time":782465,"text":"who was still growing when he died at the age of 24"},{"time":785516,"text":"and he was 8 foot 11."},{"time":788405,"text":"He had acromegaly."},{"time":789819,"text":"Do you remember the wrestler André the Giant?"},{"time":792354,"text":"Famous. He had acromegaly."},{"time":794037,"text":"There's even speculation that Abraham Lincoln had acromegaly."},{"time":798576,"text":"Anyone who's unusually tall,"},{"time":799654,"text":"that's the first explanation we come up with."},{"time":802407,"text":"And acromegaly has a very distinct set of side effects"},{"time":806402,"text":"associated with it,"},{"time":807627,"text":"principally having to do with vision."},{"time":811189,"text":"The pituitary tumor, as it grows,"},{"time":814485,"text":"often starts to compress the visual nerves in your brain,"},{"time":818533,"text":"with the result that people with acromegaly"},{"time":821037,"text":"have either double vision or they are profoundly nearsighted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":826508,"text":"So when people have started to speculate"},{"time":829101,"text":"about what might have been wrong with Goliath,"},{"time":832332,"text":"they've said, \"Wait a minute,"},{"time":833243,"text":"he looks and sounds an awful lot like someone"},{"time":836433,"text":"who has acromegaly.\""},{"time":838006,"text":"And that would also explain so much of what was strange"},{"time":840990,"text":"about his behavior that day."},{"time":843117,"text":"Why does he move so slowly"},{"time":844938,"text":"and have to be escorted down into the valley floor"},{"time":848466,"text":"by an attendant?"},{"time":849825,"text":"Because he can't make his way on his own."},{"time":852813,"text":"Why is he so strangely oblivious to David"},{"time":856070,"text":"that he doesn't understand that David's not going to fight him"},{"time":858719,"text":"until the very last moment?"},{"time":860866,"text":"Because he can't see him."},{"time":863375,"text":"When he says, \"Come to me that I might feed your flesh"},{"time":866692,"text":"to the birds of the heavens and the beasts of the field,\""},{"time":869188,"text":"the phrase \"come to me\" is a hint also of his vulnerability."},{"time":873832,"text":"Come to me because I can't see you."},{"time":876816,"text":"And then there's, \"Am I a dog that you should come to me with sticks?\""},{"time":882030,"text":"He sees two sticks when David has only one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":887360,"text":"So the Israelites up on the mountain ridge"},{"time":890324,"text":"looking down on him thought he was"},{"time":892521,"text":"this extraordinarily powerful foe."},{"time":895632,"text":"What they didn't understand was that"},{"time":897608,"text":"the very thing that was the source of his apparent strength"},{"time":900905,"text":"was also the source of his greatest weakness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":904660,"text":"And there is, I think, in that,"},{"time":906617,"text":"a very important lesson for all of us."},{"time":909822,"text":"Giants are not as strong and powerful as they seem."},{"time":913684,"text":"And sometimes the shepherd boy has a sling in his pocket."}]},{"cues":[{"time":917173,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":918960,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}